    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拯救世界的并非勇者的利刃，而是剪辑师手中的鼠标光标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在本作中，你将担任一名专属视频“剪辑师”，负责伪造连地下城都通关不了的“废柴勇士”的战斗视频。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >受雇于这毫无实力却虚荣心爆棚的勇士，你的任务是制作出华丽无比的“通关视频”，营造出大获全胜的假象。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要深入分析敌人的攻击套路等预判情报，并在时间轴上巧妙编排勇士有限的动作片段，亲手谱写出一出“必胜剧本”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一边满足镇民们的欢呼，一边满足那个渴望多巴胺刺激的魔王。你必须在7天之内造就一段虚假的英雄传说，并以此拯救世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>开战前的必胜策略设计</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在视频编辑器中，敌人的攻击模式和干扰行为将以“预录制素材”的形式呈现。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家在战斗开始前，需要预先浏览时间轴，精准掌握敌人的进攻时机，并以此制定相应的反制方案。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4311000/extras/e5428b0d6050305931d95f464f3313ef.poster.avif?t=1770440612\" width=1170 height=660 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4311000/extras/e5428b0d6050305931d95f464f3313ef.webm?t=1770440612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4311000/extras/e5428b0d6050305931d95f464f3313ef.mp4?t=1770440612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>片段编辑</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 8 刻的时间轴上布置「移动」、「近战攻击」、「远程攻击」、「防御」片段，以此设计勇士的动作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4311000/extras/5ef280ea5c3a15b90854fa016db47dce.poster.avif?t=1770440612\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4311000/extras/5ef280ea5c3a15b90854fa016db47dce.webm?t=1770440612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4311000/extras/5ef280ea5c3a15b90854fa016db47dce.mp4?t=1770440612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特效 (VFX)</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >编辑的核心在于修饰！将平凡的移动瞬间变为“瞬间移动”，或将微不足道的攻击化为“暴击”来制服敌人。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >内存太小了？别担心！只要达成“填满时间轴”、“有效攻击 2 次以上”、“未受伤害”等优化条件，可用内存就会增加。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4311000/extras/893c6d271a1eaa05f808cdc5ef6bf6fb.poster.avif?t=1770440612\" width=1170 height=660 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4311000/extras/893c6d271a1eaa05f808cdc5ef6bf6fb.webm?t=1770440612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4311000/extras/893c6d271a1eaa05f808cdc5ef6bf6fb.mp4?t=1770440612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >由“剪辑”书写的通关传说</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验一下勇士那厚颜无耻的委托邮件，与电脑桌面上铺天盖地的英雄赞歌新闻之间的反差感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然现实中的勇者只会落荒而逃，但通过这场骗局，将其包装成救世英雄的重任，全在你的指尖。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4311000/extras/3c423f3757d02f8947668fbe3337ffd5.poster.avif?t=1770440612\" width=1170 height=661 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4311000/extras/3c423f3757d02f8947668fbe3337ffd5.mp4?t=1770440612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
